TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT RPT_PRCS_NB , RPT_CLNT_SHORT_NME , RPT_TYP_CD , CORP_CD , RPT_PRCS_STAT_CD , STMT_ID , STMT_START_DT , STMT_END_DT , RPT_START_BILL_PRD , LAST_RBAT_BILL_PRD , RPT_PRCS_TYP_CD , FREQ_CD , BILL_RNG_CD , STMT_RNG_CD , TXN_SET_CD , CLM_SET_CD , FMT_CD , BLD_TRG_FLE_NME FROM $$MVS_DB2_OWNER_WF.VW_RBAT_CLNT_RPT_CNTL WHERE (rpt_clnt_short_nme, rpt_typ_cd,RPT_PRCS_NB) IN (SELECT rpt_clnt_short_nme, rpt_typ_cd,MIN(RPT_PRCS_NB) rpt_prcs_nb FROM $$MVS_DB2_OWNER_WF.VW_RBAT_CLNT_RPT_CNTL WHERE RPT_PRCS_TYP_CD IN (51,52) AND RPT_PRCS_STAT_CD = 'R1' AND (rpt_clnt_short_nme,rpt_typ_cd) NOT IN (SELECT rpt_clnt_short_nme, rpt_typ_cd FROM $$MVS_DB2_OWNER_WF.VW_RBAT_CLNT_RPT_CNTL WHERE RPT_PRCS_STAT_CD in('P2','F2')) GROUP BY rpt_clnt_short_nme, rpt_typ_cd)
